h2 Calling Methods Dynamically

p 
  span.mk-blue Dynamic Dispatch
  | ：我們可以使用send來呼叫method。

pre
  code.ruby
    | class A
        def say_hi
          "Hi"
        end
        
        def say_hello
          "Hello"
        end
      end

      a = A.new
      
      p a.say_hi # Hi
      p a.say_hello # Hello
      
      ['hi', 'hello'].each do |what|
    = "\n" + '  p a.send("say_#{what}")' + "\n"
