h3 Privacy Matters

p 
  | send可以用來呼叫private method，不過能大越大，責任越重，你可以呼叫不代表你能呼叫。
pre
  code.ruby
    | class A
        private
        def think
          "Hmmmm..."
        end
      end

      a = A.new

      p a.think # private method `think' called for #<A:0x007fdd20982588> (NoMethodError)
      p a.send(:think) # Hmmmm...

