h3 respond_to_missing?

p 
  | 使用ghost method建立的method，對 
  code
    | respond_to?
  | 是沒有反應的。
  
pre
  code.ruby
    | class A
        def method_missing(method, *arg)
          if method =~ /say_(.*)/
            $1.capitalize
          else
            super
          end
        end
      end

      a = A.new

      p a.say_hi # Hi
      p a.respond_to?(:say_hi) # false

p 
  code
    | respond_to?
  | 會去呼叫 
  code
    | respond_to_missing?
  | ，而 
  code
    | respond_to_missing?
  | 預設就是用來處理ghost method，理論上如果你建立了ghost method，要記得一並覆寫 
  code
    | respond_to_missing?
  | ，讓它對ghost method可以回傳true。
  
pre
  code.ruby
    | class A
        def method_missing(method, *arg)
          if method =~ /say_(.*)/
            $1.capitalize
          else
            super
          end
        end

        def respond_to_missing?(method, include_private = false)
          if method =~ /say_(.*)/
            return true
          else
            super
          end
        end
      end

      a = A.new

      p a.say_hi # Hi
      p a.respond_to?(:say_hi) # true

